{"word":"εὐθυμέω","slug":"εὐθυμέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εὐθυμέω</b></el> <el>(εὐθῡμέω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:εὔθυμος'><el>εὔθυμος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be of good cheer</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b>:— <i>to be gracious</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to make cheerful, cheer, delight</i>, <el>τινά</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be cheerful</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}